Name: aelf - Breaking News!!!
Description:
aelf Mainet Token Swap Airdrop is worth up to 27,000,000 mainnet $ELF tokens (~$ 12,000,000).

About aelf

aelf is a decentralized self-evolving cloud computing network to establish a Blockchain infrastructure for various commercial requirements, providing developers with a versatile developing template for free, including consensus mechanism, communication protocol, smart contract, and other modules. Developers could access the aelf ecosystem quickly, conveniently, and efficiently. Meanwhile, aelf can also accommodate DApps of other public chains such as Ethereum and Polkadot. It also aggregates various star projects as an app store to become a safe, efficient, autonomous, stable, easy-to-use, and transparent new value financial system. aelf can interact with Bitcoin, Ethereum, and other Blockchain systems utilize its versatile oracle to enhance the heterogeneous cross-chain function becoming an Ethereum Layer 2 in practice.
Step-by-Step Guide:
aelf team has decided to launch the mainnet swap on September 9, 2021, at 12:00 PM (GMT+8).
The event will last for three months. During the event, users can replace their ERC20 ELF tokens with mainnet ELF tokens at the rate of 1:1. (Mainnet Token Swap Tutorial)
In gratitude to aelf users, aelf will send an additional 5% mainnet ELF airdrop in real-time. Swap users can get the reward by completing the token swap on the aelf website or through the eligible exchanges in the first 15 days of the event, which is from 12:00 P.M. September 9th to 12:00 PM September 23rd GMT+8 (More Info here).
